  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个时序图，展示kikwi-core在零售收银场景下如何处理优惠券系统的持久化流程。核心是从同步任务执行到最终事件发布的完整链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "kikwi-core",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到涉及多个子系统：优惠券系统、订单管理、客户忠诚度。这几个模块在时序上是什么关系？是UoW统一协调吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UnitOfWork",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，UnitOfWork是核心协调者。kikwi-core先执行同步任务，然后创建UoW实例，在同步代码块里累积订单管理的变更。注意这里有个关键点：同步块结束后才触发真正的提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UoW",
        "bloco síncrono",
        "Acumula alterações"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出Core自调用的同步任务执行，然后连到UoW的创建和变更累积。这里我用注释标注一下同步块的结束位置。接下来是提交到Repository？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core-Core",
        "Core-UoW",
        "Note over Core"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，commit操作要指向ProcessExecutionRepository，而且这里涉及客户忠诚度的数据。但真正的持久化是Repository去操作MongoDB，需要展开成一个显式的事务块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "ProcessExecutionRepository",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "MongoDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "事务内部有三步：更新ProcessInstance、处理ExecutableTasks的创建删除、还有插入event_outbox。第三步的criticalEvents是做什么用的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Atualiza ProcessInstance",
        "Cria/Apaga ExecutableTasks",
        "event_outbox",
        "criticalEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "criticalEvents是最终要发布的事件，先存到outbox表里保证事务原子性。等MongoDB事务提交成功后，Core才会异步调用EventPublisher。这个publisher也是优惠券系统的组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "criticalEvents",
        "event_outbox",
        "EventPublisher",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了MongoDB内部的三步自调用，还有Repository返回的commit成功确认。现在加Publisher的调用——等等，我标注的是publishEvents(Retail_PointOfSale)，但之前说Publisher属于CouponSystem？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Publisher",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "你发现了问题。Publisher确实是CouponSystem的组件，但发布的事件应该关联到Retail_PointOfSale这个上下文。让我确认一下……对，参数应该是Retail_PointOfSale，但Publisher的标注要保持Retail_CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventPublisher",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "publishEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，Participant标注为EventPublisher (Retail_CouponSystem)，调用参数是Retail_PointOfSale。最后Publisher返回是立即返回对吧？不需要等实际发布完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Publisher---Core",
        "Retorno Imediato"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Retorno Imediato说明是异步 fire-and-forget。整个流程的关键就是：同步块攒变更→事务提交保证一致性→异步发事件。检查一下，Repository到MongoDB的调用应该是同步阻塞的，用实线加号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repository-+MongoDB",
        "INICIAR TRANSAÇÃO",
        "COMMIT TRANSAÇÃO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下箭头样式：Core到Repository的commit是实线加号（激活），Repository到MongoDB也是实线加号，MongoDB内部三步是自调用。返回都用虚线。还有哪里需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core-+Repository",
        "Repository-+MongoDB",
        "MongoDB-MongoDB",
        "虚线返回"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来都对了。最后确认Participant名称：Core要显示为kikwi-core (Retail_PointOfSale)，UoW和Publisher都要带Retail_CouponSystem后缀。这样业务边界就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "kikwi-core<br(Retail_PointOfSale)",
        "UnitOfWork (Retail_CouponSystem)",
        "EventPublisher (Retail_CouponSystem)"
      ],
